8 An Act relating to boards and commissions; amending
68 O.S. 2021, Section 2357.7, which relates to credit
9 for investments in qualified venture capital
companies; removing certain authority for the
10 Oklahoma Capital Investment Board; amending 74 O.S.
2021, Section 85.42, as amended by Section 9, Chapter
11 336, O.S.L. 2025 (74 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section 85.42),
which relates to the exceptions on the one-year
12 limitation on entering contracts with certain
persons; removing certain reference; amending 74 O.S.
13 2021, Section 3601.1, as last amended by Section 36,
Chapter 29, O.S.L. 2023 (74 O.S. Supp. 2025, Section
14 3601.1), which relates to employees; deleting
reference to the Oklahoma Capital Investment Board
15 allowable employees; updating statutory language;
updating statutory reference; repealing 63 O.S. 2021,
16 Sections 1-236, 1-237, 1-237.1, and 1-238, which
relate to definitions used in the Joint Legislative
17 Committee for Review of Coordination of Efforts for
Prevention of Adolescent Pregnancy and Sexually
18 Transmitted Diseases, the coordinating council for
the joint committee, the Postponing Sexual
19 Involvement for Young Teens program, and the state
plan for the committee; repealing 70 O.S. 2021,
20 Sections 3-117.1, 3-117.2, and 3-117.3, which relate
to the School Finance Review Commission Act, creation
21 of the School Finance Review Commission, and duties
of the Commission; providing an effective date; and
22 declaring an emergency.
